{"tid":2300064,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個係馬路撚鳩女司機既經歷","createTime":"2020-11-25T08:31:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T18:15:31.000Z","uid":157483,"like":30,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6e8dcdc92ddf74b1bd6b916c90e8effa01ffef","tid":2300064,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:31:25.000Z","msg":"之前有次坐朋友車<br />\n我朋友揸掃把佬liberty<br />\n前面有架p牌波子 快線撚 又揸撚到左搖右擺咁<br />\n咁我朋友咪cut線爬佢<br />\n係隔離線並排果陣，我一望 果然係女司機 仲要p牌，仲要成車女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該係唔知邊個八婆勾掂條水魚買架波子比佢揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後成班八婆諗住威<br />\n我咪即刻嗌：傻閪就咪學人揸車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爬完佢頭之後，我望後鏡 唔知條傻閪比我激親定真係手車太垃圾 控唔好個軚<br />\n車頭出左界撞到隔離線架林寶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後我即刻伸隻手出去比個👎🏻佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心諗今次你成班姐妹一齊做雞都賠唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同我朋友真係笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd1a7173fe962bc4fca3227a16403bca7cdf267","tid":2300064,"uid":25727,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:34:15.000Z","msg":"趁我條女揸車嗰陣我就揸佢個波 有時仲撩吓佢下面等佢濕哂咁樣撚鳩佢<img src=\"/